    <title>UTC 邮件客户端配置 - 安卓 - Gmail</title>
    <url>/2020/03/31/utcmail/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="UTC-邮件客户端配置-安卓-Gmail"><a href="#UTC-邮件客户端配置-安卓-Gmail" class="headerlink" title="UTC 邮件客户端配置 - 安卓 - Gmail"></a>UTC 邮件客户端配置 - 安卓 - Gmail</h1><a id="more"></a>

<ol>
<li>打开Gmail，点击右上角的头像以打开账户管理；</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQY5wt" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQY5wt.jpg" alt="GQY5wt.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="2">
<li>选择“添加其他账号”； </li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQYITP" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQYITP.jpg" alt="GQYITP.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="3">
<li>选择“其他“；</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQYTFf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQYTFf.jpg" alt="GQYTFf.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="4">
<li>填入UTC邮箱地址；</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQY7Y8" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQY7Y8.jpg" alt="GQY7Y8.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="5">
<li>在类型中选择IMAP；</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQY4eI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQY4eI.jpg" alt="GQY4eI.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="6">
<li>填入UTC邮箱密码；</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQYHfS" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQYHfS.jpg" alt="GQYHfS.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="7">
<li>此处用户名为ENT登陆用户名，服务器地址为<code>imaps.utc.fr</code></li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQYLlQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQYLlQ.jpg" alt="GQYLlQ.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="8">
<li>此处用户名为ENT登陆用户名，打开“需求登录”，服务器地址为<code>smtps.utc.fr</code></li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQYOyj" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQYOyj.jpg" alt="GQYOyj.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="9">
<li>剩余为用户自定义设置，根据自己喜好填写即可；</li>
</ol>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/GQYXOs" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img data-src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/31/GQYXOs.jpg" alt="GQYXOs.jpg"></a></p>
<hr>
<ol start="10">
<li>教程至此结束，如有疑惑可以在评论区提出。</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
