    <title>MD语法笔记</title>
    <url>/2018/12/27/note/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>之前一直用 HTML 写博文的我真的是勤快过头了，现在才发现 Hexo 有 MD 支持。</p>
<p>在这里简单记下 MD 的语法以备后续使用。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>2020/04/01 根据<a href="spec.commonmark.org/">MarkDown 标准网站</a>更新。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<ol>
<li>自动目录</li>
</ol>
<a id="more"></a>

<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[TOC]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="2">
<li>多级标题</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">一级标题</span><br><span class="line">====</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 四级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### 五级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="3">
<li>字体样式</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**这是加粗的文字**</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_这是倾斜的文字_</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**_这是斜体加粗的文字_*</span>*  </span><br><span class="line">~~这是加删除线的文字~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="4">
<li>引用</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 这是引用的内容</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; &gt; 这是引用的内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; 这是引用的内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="5">
<li>分割线</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">___</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="6">
<li>超链接</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">超链接名 1</span>](<span class="link">超链接地址 "超链接title"</span>)&#123;:target="\_blank"&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片alt</span>](<span class="link">图片地址 "图片title"</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">[图片 alt(图片地址)</span>]](超链接地址)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="7">
<li>列表</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3. </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">4. </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line">   1. 列表内容</span><br><span class="line">   - 列表内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<ol start="8">
<li>表格</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">表格的语句上一行必须为空行。</span><br><span class="line">|表头|表头|表头|</span><br><span class="line">|-|:-:|-:| #这行分割表头与内容，标记居中、左、右。</span><br><span class="line">|居左|居中|居右|</span><br><span class="line">|如果说话稍微多一点的话|就可以看出来差别了|我希望是这样没有问题的。|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>表头</th>
<th align="center">表头</th>
<th align="right">表头</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>居左</td>
<td align="center">居中</td>
<td align="right">居右</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>如果说话稍微多一点的话</td>
<td align="center">就可以看出来差别了</td>
<td align="right">我希望是这样没有问题的。</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<hr>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`代码内容`</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">“<span class="code">```” #这为了显示，本没有引号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">代码块用两行“```”包起来，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">我想在这里是看不出来了……</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">“```” #这为了显示，本没有引号</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><code>代码内容</code></p>
<hr>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[x] 选项一</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[ ] 选项二</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[ ] 选项三</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 选项一</li>
<li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 选项二</li>
<li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 选项三</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">“<span class="code">```flow” #这为了显示，本没有引号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">st=&gt;start: 开始</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">op1=&gt;operation: 程序</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">sub2=&gt;subroutine: 子程序</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">cond3=&gt;condition: 是或否？</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">io4=&gt;inputoutput: 输入</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">e=&gt;end: 结束</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">st-&gt;op1-&gt;cond4</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">cond3(yes,up)-&gt;io4(down)-&gt;e</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">cond3(no,left)-&gt;sub2(right)-&gt;op</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">“```” #这为了显示，本没有引号</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>好吧，不支持。</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">xxx@xxx.com</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><span class="exturl" data-url="bWFpbHRvOiYjeDc4OyYjMTIwOyYjeDc4OyYjNjQ7JiMxMjA7JiN4Nzg7JiMxMjA7JiM0NjsmIzk5OyYjeDZmOyYjMTA5Ow==" title="mailto:&#x78;&#120;&#x78;&#64;&#120;&#x78;&#120;&#46;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;">&#x78;&#120;&#x78;&#64;&#120;&#x78;&#120;&#46;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;<i class="fa fa-external-link"></i></span></p>
<hr>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Markdown</span><br><span class="line">: 轻量级文本标记语言，可以转换成 html，pdf 等格式</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">代码块定义</span><br><span class="line">: 代码块定义……</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">        var a = 10; #保持空一行与 递进缩进</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

